a.n: Pitchfork Music Festival: Run The Jewels

p.k: Run the Jewels, rap group founded by rapper/producer EL-P and rapper Killer Mike in 2013, delivered an electrifying performance at the 2015 Pitchfork Music Festival in Paris.
p.d: Run the Jewels, rap group founded by rapper/producer EL-P and rapper Killer Mike in 2013, delivered an electrifying performance at the 2015 Pitchfork Music Festival in Paris. The group's three homonymous albums have been hailed by the public and critics alike. As part of this concert at the Grande Halle de la Villette, the duo is accompanied by DJ Trackstar.
